    "en": {
      "title": "The President is still in Sri Lanka",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Speaker Mahinda Yapa Abeywardena said that President Gotabaya Rajapaksa will continue to stay in Sri Lanka. He has said this in a telephone discussion with India's ANI news service.",
        "He told the BBC that the President had left the country. He also stated that what was mentioned with the news service was a mistake.",
        "Here A.N.I. The news service has asked where the president and prime minister are.",
        "In reply to that, the Speaker mentioned that both of them are still in Sri Lanka."
      ],
